author: Jorge Alonso
title: Annoying Falcons Fan Is Running Around And Trolling Packers Fans By Knocking Off Their Cheesehead Hats At Stadium
text:
The Green Bay Packers are getting absolutely crushed by the Atlanta Falcons in the NFC championship game. To add insult to injury, one annoying Falcons fan is trolling Packers fans at the Georgia Dome by running around and knocking their stupid looking cheeseheads hats off their head. 







This is going to end with a Packers fan knocking her out. 
H/T Busted Coverage
